may have seen Weave.jl, R Markdown, JupyterBook. Basically the fundamental idea is that we want to

00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:40.919
create a scientific and technical publishing system that uses markdown and enhances it with

00:01:40.919 --> 00:01:45.440
features that are required for scientific communication. So first and foremost of those

