for scientific discourse is very broad. There's R, there's Julia, there's Python, there's Scala,

00:03:00.800 --> 00:03:07.479
and there will be many more. And what we really wanted to do was take all of the experience you

00:03:07.479 --> 00:03:14.080
had with R Markdown, build a new system kind of reimagined with the benefit of hindsight and make

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:21.279
that system fundamentally multi-language and multi-engine. So not tied to R in any way and

