get into more of the mechanics and the how and the what I wanted to talk a little bit about the

00:03:39.220 --> 00:03:46.419
goals of the project. One is this idea of computational documents and that is documents

00:03:46.419 --> 00:03:51.100
that incorporate the source code required for their production directly inside the document.

